reviewText:
Really great collection. Nicole Conn is clearly the pre-eminent writer/director/producer
for the lesbian community. These are all lesbian-positive but still 50% unhappy
endings.
Nicole Conn knows how to make great movies. Really enjoyed them a lot of heart.

The audio effects on Cynara DVD were not the best quality.  Ambience noise was louder than the actresses voices.  Claire of the Moon had everything on it from drama to comedy.  The Perfect Ending and Elena Undone they just captivated my heart.
Beautifully sculptured films. Capturing the essence and nuances  of what a woman feels and who she is
